data.description: If you’re looking for the best location and true St Pete living this home is for you! This 2 bed 1 bath Central Oak Park bungalow is filled with warmth and plenty of natural light for your plant babes and mental well being. The hardwood floors have been restored throughout so they are lookin' fresh. Updated kitchen is complete with the butcher block eat in area and “knock knock” fridge so you always know when you’re running low on snacks. The coziest spot is the bonus room in the back of the house for a meditators dream where you can relax and unwind and do some yoga. Attached garage has in law suite potential with separate entrance. Alley access with driveway in the back. And let’s not forget the lemon tree for some fresh squeezed lemonade on a hot Florida day! Centrally located just minutes from Pass a Grille Beach, Downtown St Pete and Downtown Gulfport. Schedule a showing today!
